Building vim/gvim with ruby:
    cygwin libraries needed:
        - ncurses devel
        - gtk2 devel
        - xt devel
        - xpm devel
        - cairo devel
        - xmu devel
        - xorg macros, xorg config files
        - pkg-config

    configure command:
        ./configure --prefix=<prefix> --with-features=huge --enable-gui=gtk2 --enable-rubyinterp

